description: We were supposed to go to Mt Tamalpais this morning, but after checking the fog coverage and some people sleeping in, we settled for a closer option on this side of the bay. Ended up in Mount Sutro by UCSF and we were not disappointed with how well the light was diffused by the leaves in this forest-y hiking trail. Just a humble reminder that maybe the adventure is closer than you know.
